metadata.name: Hektor's Stronghold
metadata.description:
The cruelty of Hektor's Dynasty has been witnessed by ages upon ages. Some says he is like a black cloud or storm. But there must be someome who could help the civilization to get protected from his brutish culture.
Local folks spam about a beautiful yet deadly queen whom Hektor married after killing her family members and acquired her kingdom, is the sole reason of Hektor's mysterious death. A cut throat deadly assassin residing in the palace whome Hektor wasn't even alerted about. On the full moon, silence prevailed everywhere, those cool yet sharp breezes channeling through his Citadel, making the king to make a move on the queen. That night no one heard anything from both of em. Next morning, guards declared the country, Next morning guards came up with a statement, "King has been shot dead by his enemies and the ritual is about to begin" On this date, his castel commonly known as Hektor's Stronghold has being abandoned.
